data.chText: 恐怖症，恐惧症（无名的极度恐惧）
data.enText: a strong unreasonable fear of sth
He has a phobia about flying.
(in nouns) a strong unreasonable fear or hatred of a particular thing

simple_means.memory_skill: phob 恐惧；厌恶 + ia 表名词 → 十分厌恶

means: 恐怖症(无名的极度恐惧)

tr: an anxiety disorder characterized by extreme and irrational fear of simple things or social situations
example: phobic disorder is a general term for all phobias

value.def: A phobia is a very strong irrational fear or hatred of something.

example.ex: The man had a phobia about flying.

rootsaffixes.indicate: = to fear, to dislike 恐惧；厌恶
rootsaffixes.title: phob

partsOfSpeech.dec: acro 高 + phob 恐惧；厌恶 + ia 某种病 → 恐高症
hydro 水 + phob 恐惧；厌恶 + ia 某种病 → 恐水症
phob 恐惧；厌恶 + ia 某种病 → 十分厌恶
